## Changelog

### 5.0.2 (05.10.2023)
- Autocomplete deny for secret settings fields

### 5.0.1 (05.10.2023)
- Updated node packages to latest versions

### 5.0.0 (05.10.2023)
- Moved secrets to Redis storage
- Added update fields for secrets to settings page
- Added that if GPT response is unclear, it defaults to result is true
- Removed pwd.json file, changed default password

### 4.2.1 (30.09.2023)
- Added new component Loadingspinner
- Added better User Feedback by applying error colors to fields of scheduling
- Added Alert and Snackbar for better User Feedback

### 4.1.0 (30.09.2023)
- Added new functionality to delete scheduled tasks
- Add uuid 4 to generate unique ids
- Added to each task a unique id
- Added better styling to scheduled tasks for better distinction
- Changed some naming
- Autosizing of textarea in GPT Response

### 3.0.0 (27.09.2023)
- Add redisclient also to ai project
- Edited envswitcher to include redis client addresses
- Added new Settingspage to be able to edit GPT Request from frontend
- Inserted GPT Request in Redis

### 2.1.3 (24.09.2023)
- Changed request text to gpt

